name: ext-msgpack-rs
docs:
MessagePack encode/decode with ext.data_model integration.

Modules:
- ext.msgpack
- ext.msgpack.data_model
- ext.msgpack.tests

Usage:
- Add dependency: x07 pkg add ext-msgpack-rs@0.1.2 --sync
- Import ext.msgpack.data_model.

Notes:
- Determinism: pure
- Data model integration: ext.msgpack.data_model
- Numbers beyond i32 range are encoded via MessagePack ext types.
